	quest.056C707476E4BA33.quest_subtitle: "You will require either of these to insert fuel into the inserter"
	quest.056C707476E4BA33.title: "Inserting fuel "
	quest.05BC7CBC05B15830.quest_subtitle: "Pushes heat to a small area, be careful to not pump too much heat.."
	quest.05BFBACBB2337231.quest_desc: [
		"&7Andesite&r is a very abundant stone that you can find in large pockets underground. They blend really well with the stone texture, so keep your eyes open for them"
		""
		"&6Casings&r can be crafted by right clicking with a valid alloy or ingot on any stripped variant of log or wood"
	]
	quest.05BFBACBB2337231.quest_subtitle: "&7Andesite Alloy&r is a material used in &7Andesite Casings&r and simple kinetic blocks, which serves as an entry point to the mechanical components of &6&lCreate&r"
	quest.05BFBACBB2337231.title: "&7Andesite&r, the Foundation"
	quest.063D47D4F61457BC.quest_subtitle: "A &6Schedule&r lets you schedule trains so that mobs or &6Blaze Burners&r can drive them"
	quest.06653E21053ACDF6.quest_subtitle: "A &cPowered Latch&r that toggles on when receiving a redstone signal on one side and off when receiving a signal on another side"
	quest.071F9DA863D5E146.quest_subtitle: "Start by making bread slices with Farmer’s Delight’s cutting board, or craft a burger bun. Place a Sandwich Station, put a bread slice or bun on top, and begin adding ingredients of your choice. Along with food, potions can also be added. When you’re done, break the sandwich to collect it. You can place sandwiches anywhere by shift-right-clicking"
	quest.071F9DA863D5E146.title: "Obtain your Chicken Sandwich"
	quest.07680D1563629D55.quest_subtitle: "A &6Depot&r is really just a belt that doesn't move"
