	quest.139DAA6E8CF4267A.quest_desc: [
		"At the bottom of the inventory, you may have noticed a search bar"
		""
		"This is the &dJust Enough Items&r, or &dJEI&r, search bar"
		""
		"If you type \"Wood\", for example, the &dJEI &ritem list at the right of the screen will show all items with \"Wood\" in the name"
		""
		"Adding a @ at the start of the search query will show the items from a specific mod, for example @Create"
		""
		"To favorite an item, press &bA &rwhile hovering over it in the &dJEI &ritem list, and it will appear in the left panel until you press &bA on it again"
	]
	quest.139DAA6E8CF4267A.quest_subtitle: "Read my description!"
	quest.139DAA6E8CF4267A.title: "&bJust Enough Items (JEI)"
	quest.13D4FF6929AE8D8F.quest_subtitle: "A &6Extendo Grip&r allows for increased reach for block mining and entity striking"
	quest.13D833C11A71B131.quest_subtitle: "Can be used for feeding the Blaze Forger and Blaze Enchanter, or for crafting other items"
	quest.13D833C11A71B131.title: "&2Craft Block of Experience."
	quest.14E0A5E1BA5DFA57.title: "Generating heat"
	quest.14F9238BF932A5EB.title: "Capture Chicken by using Roost"
	quest.152333F57A5C1913.quest_subtitle: "A &6Rolling Mill&r is for milling raw materials into useful components, like rods and wires"
	quest.155F388D56FB4A5F.quest_subtitle: "&6Mechanical Saws&r can fell trees or allow contraptions to fell trees, as well as perform recipes like cutting blocks or stripping &aLogs&r"
	quest.155FBDDA1C6194CA.quest_subtitle: "A &6Contraption Control&r let you turn off parts of contraptions while they are formed"
	quest.157DAE6EC4155F82.quest_subtitle: "Can be find in caves, or mixed with Honey and Lava"
	quest.157DAE6EC4155F82.title: "Obtain Limestone"
	quest.15F53F788D18518A.title: "Build Industrial Blasting"
	quest.160E4D26B4D8A901.title: "Materials for Crates"
	quest.163D0CE9361628FA.title: "Engine"
	quest.16C68DA939A28FCB.quest_subtitle: "Mechanical crafters are needed to make the inactive blaze core item"
	quest.16C68DA939A28FCB.title: "Activate Mechanical Crafter"
	quest.16CD1CC9F70A91AF.quest_subtitle: "An &6Adjustable Chain Gearshift&r can be used to halve or double the rotational speed of connected chain drives when receiving a &credstone&r signal"
	quest.1742597D48E37800.quest_desc: [
		"&6&lCreate&r offers great guides for most of its items by hovering over them in &d&lJEI&r or in your inventory and holding down &eW&r to &bponder&r the item, but sometimes it's best just to test each thing out"
		""
		"{image:allofcreate:textures/qb_image1.png width:397 height:140 align:center fit:true}"
		""
		"Because of this, the chapter is mostly focused on letting you know what exists and giving you a rough outline of the progression of the mod, but at the same time, it will not handhold you all the way to the end since &6&lCreate&r is a sandbox mechanic mod"
	]
	quest.1742597D48E37800.quest_subtitle: "&b&lAll of Create&r is based around &6&lCreate&r, a steampunk mod that lets you build contraptions and automate most things you can think of"
	quest.1742597D48E37800.title: "Welcome to &b&lAll of Create: Aeronautics&r!"
	quest.175099CF5696829E.quest_desc: [
		"&9Tasks &rare things that need to be done to complete a quest. If a task is an item, clicking on it will show its recipe"
		""
		"&6Rewards &rare what you get after completing all &9Tasks&r. Click to claim"
		""
		"The pin icon at the top left will pin a quest to your screen"
	]
