	quest.19166D31F298D0D5.quest_subtitle: "A &6Display Board&r is basically an advanced sign that updates faster if provided with higher &6RPM&r. It's like the bulletin boards you see in train stations"
	quest.19183F380B49F31C.quest_subtitle: "A &6Encased Fan&r is a very versatile machine that can pull and push entities, as well as wash, haunt, blast, and smoke items"
