		"When you click the square at the top left of your player display, your &8Curios &rslots will become visible. Some items, such as Elytras and Totems can be equipped here"
	]
	quest.2958CA7FA6FD3E4F.quest_subtitle: "Read my description!"
	quest.2958CA7FA6FD3E4F.title: "&2Inventory"
	quest.29649C654117D56A.quest_subtitle: "An &cAnalog Lever&r can be set to output any redstone level. It's basically an upgraded version of the basic lever"
	quest.29EFF7AED691682B.quest_subtitle: "A &6Wrench&r lets you instantly break most &6&lCreate&r blocks by &eShift + Right-clicking&r. And rotate them by &eRight-clicking&r. Your all-purpose friend you'll never leave home without again"
	quest.29F3FCDB8B20E164.quest_subtitle: "A gearbox with shafts on all 6 sides. Conceptually uses the same internal mechanism as Parallel Gearbox, so top and bottom spins at half speed"
	quest.29F3FCDB8B20E164.title: "Obtain 6-way Gearbox."
	quest.2A0F7A2AA1C0E9C1.quest_subtitle: "A basic filter"
	quest.2A1B37D9EA24777B.quest_subtitle: "+25% Engine power +50% Fuel requirement. For when a Lava Engine just isn't enough by itself"
	quest.2A5D792CD3695430.quest_subtitle: "Place near the Block of Experience during a thunderstorm"
	quest.2A5D792CD3695430.title: "&6Craft Lighting rod."
	quest.2AB0806AA6A7076C.quest_subtitle: "An upgraded version of the &6Copper Diving Helmet&r"
	quest.2AC910A3CE221B33.quest_subtitle: "A clutch that is uncoupled unless powered"
	quest.2AC910A3CE221B33.title: "Obtain Clutch"
	quest.2B51030D87EFB0A2.quest_subtitle: "-20% Fuel requirement. For getting that little bit more juice out of your charcoal"
	quest.2BC0A0977CD94919.quest_subtitle: "Place it into a depot and wait for the Conduit Cage to convert it into Prismarine Shards."
	quest.2BC0A0977CD94919.title: "Obtain flint"
	quest.2BC564546A48616B.quest_subtitle: "A &6Mechanical Bearing&r allows for contraptions that rotate around a point in space, particularly useful for farms"
	quest.2C3CD6663D38750A.quest_subtitle: "The &6Mechanical Press&r is used for processing items provided beneath it on a depot or belt, or in a basin to compact"
	quest.2C770179FF6B1F73.title: "Obtain Trading Depot"
	quest.2C8EF8E65133D178.quest_desc: ["The &6Empty Blaze Burner&r can be filled by &eRight-clicking&r it on either a &6Blaze Spawner&r or a &6Blaze&r"]
	quest.2C8EF8E65133D178.quest_subtitle: "In order to get &eBrass&r, you're going to need to heat a &6Mechanical Mixer&r that's mixing &6Copper&r and &7Zinc&r ingots"
	quest.2C8EF8E65133D178.title: "Blaze Burner"
	quest.2C96A172ACC0226F.quest_subtitle: "Remember to cover your rods before activating... or it's going to be Chernobyl."
	quest.2C96A172ACC0226F.title: "Reactor 101"
	quest.2CC43C68A8EECB8D.quest_subtitle: "The densest kinetic source and endgame of regular Create for Stress Unit generation, although it also has the highest complexity, requiring a steady source of &9water&r and &6heat&r"
	quest.2CC43C68A8EECB8D.title: "Steam Engine"
	quest.2D0B2D01669E88DD.quest_subtitle: "Simply a Potato Cannon"
	quest.2D0BBF1DF08E9BE4.quest_subtitle: "+50% Takeoff speed. For when you forgot to build that extra ten blocks of your runway"
	quest.2E10D93D926631F6.quest_subtitle: "An item used to craft more advanced mechanical items"
	quest.2E31F85F781C4BCC.title: "Obtain Grapplin Whisk"
	quest.2E907AC52B8EE2E9.title: "Obtain &6Liquid Vector Thruster"
	quest.2F4D033C31346B10.quest_subtitle: "Hologram: display text or items in a hologram style"
	quest.2F4D033C31346B10.title: "Obtain Hologram Source."
	quest.2FDFF69D73F47CF8.quest_subtitle: "Fast-firing cannon fueled with gunpowder"
	quest.302167AFA048184F.quest_subtitle: "After crafting your first Chicken Sandwich, you gain access to a wide range of custom sandwich recipes, allowing you to create your own unique burgers"
	quest.302167AFA048184F.title: "Obtain Burger"
	quest.306E26FB7650939B.title: "Craft Exhaust"
	quest.3079DF976F5290C3.quest_desc: [
		"This is a custom claim system that is separate from &6OPAC&r, but integrated with its parties and allies system and claim amount"
		""
		"You can claim sub-levels (ships, aircraft, or anything) with the block using its &bGUI&r"
		""
		"{image:allofcreate:textures/qb_aeroclaims1.png width:100 height:100 align:center fit:true}"
		""
		"You will have to use Aero Claims depending on your sub-level size. Aero Claims are obtained by converting regular &6OPAC Claims&r into Aero Claims through the &bAeroClaims Menu&r"
		""
		""
		"{image:allofcreate:textures/qb-aeroclaims2.png width:100 height:100 align:center fit:true}"
	]
	quest.3079DF976F5290C3.quest_subtitle: "Used for claiming sub-levels as they are seperate from regular claims"
	quest.3088C3F2E1060189.quest_subtitle: "With both of the totem parts you can now start the assembling procedure. Along with the totem parts you will also need to add the emerald eyes of the totem. This is done by placing all the needed parts into four mechanical crafters."
	quest.309779606351AC6A.quest_subtitle: "Stores kinetic stress for later use. Retains charge in item form to enable long-distance energy transport. Battery capacity, RPM at discharge and stress impact values are all configurable"
	quest.309779606351AC6A.title: "Obtain Kinetic Battery"
	quest.30C1D45E7545FA6C.quest_subtitle: "Connect with a heat source into a boiler heater, spreads heat across all pipes evenly unless pumped."
	quest.30CF131DFA9D542D.quest_subtitle: "Transfer stress capacity from one network to another while keeping the networks separate. Guarantees that the source network will not be affected when the destination network is overstressed"
	quest.30CF131DFA9D542D.title: "Obtain Kinetic bridge"
	quest.30D7DB66D96F6059.quest_subtitle: "\"I am you, but stronger.\""
	quest.3103AA1D921B71BC.quest_subtitle: "As the name implies, &aSuper Glue&r allows you to glue blocks together. Particularly useful when making contraptions"
	quest.312320F8FF1FDF24.quest_subtitle: "An upgraded version of the &6Copper Diving Boots&r"
	quest.3163768E54FA4D87.quest_subtitle: "A kinetic source that uses the power of the wind to generate rotational force. The amount of &6SU&r generated depends on the number of sails connected to the &6Windmill&r and maxes out at 8,192 per bearing"
	quest.3163768E54FA4D87.title: "Windmill Bearing"
	quest.326B2F79F3A9D8D7.quest_subtitle: "Produce more than 1000 &6Train Tracks&r with the same &6Mechanical Press&r"
