	quest.5C251AB7110F0E5F.quest_subtitle: "&6Huge Diesel Engines&r connect to &6Shafts&r and will start generating kinetic energy once you give them some fuel"
	quest.5C583586C93CA3F7.quest_subtitle: "A similar process follows the creation of the totem's body. You saw and press a tumbaga alloy, and instead of potions, you deploy a ghast tear to give the totem regenerative powers and deploy a tumbaga alloy to seal it up."
