	quest.5FF617620A38A716.quest_subtitle: "As the name implies, &aSuper Glue&r allows you to glue blocks together. Particularly useful when making contraptions"
	quest.603AAE60ABAEB20E.quest_subtitle: "Deep Dark is an addon for Create that introduces new end-game content inspired by the Deep Dark biome, featuring rare items, resources, and powerful gear to craft using Create’s mechanics!"
