	quest.72F3965D09F3B6F0.quest_desc: ["You can press &eU&r on the &fStraw&r to see what liquids it accepts, as well as their burn times"]
	quest.72F3965D09F3B6F0.quest_subtitle: "Ever wanted to pipe liquids into your &6Blaze Burners&r? Just hand them a &fStraw&r and they'll slurp it straight from the pipe!"
